item.description: score:151 Chances: Unity Software Inc. (U) has been upgraded to a Zacks Rank #2 (Buy), reflecting growing optimism about the company’s earnings prospects. Shares of game engine maker Unity (NYSE:U) jumped 6.5% in the afternoon session after The Federal Reserve maintained its key interest rate for the third consecutive time, holding it within the targeted range of 5.
